
An example of Square In-App Payments SDK (frontend only) integration into a bare `expo` 51 `React Native` project.

UI Source code taken (adapted) from: https://github.com/square/in-app-payments-react-native-plugin/tree/master/react-native-in-app-payments-quickstart

Configuration: custom.

## Build & Run

Set up `.env.local` file with:

```
EXPO_PUBLIC_SQUARE_APP_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_SQUARE_LOCATION_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_APPLE_PAY_MERCHANT_ID=
```

### Backend Server

```bash
$ cd pkg/sqip_backend
$ RUST_LOG=debug cargo run --release
```

### iOS

```bash
$ yarn && yarn ios --device
```

### Android

```bash
$ yarn && yarn android --device
```